    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/5d4a79ef8df8f424b6c92c47a7fa5ec2.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/5d4a79ef8df8f424b6c92c47a7fa5ec2.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/5d4a79ef8df8f424b6c92c47a7fa5ec2.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/57619f2ce57b7813686d316d6a68a0e7.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/57619f2ce57b7813686d316d6a68a0e7.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/57619f2ce57b7813686d316d6a68a0e7.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >oneway.exe is a first-person investigation puzzle horror game centered on story and internet culture. Explore the digital decay found within the unfinished game of UNTITLED.exe, and solve puzzles as you begin to piece together the story of the three developers who created it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the internet horrors that haunt your past. The ones you've never heard of. They don't exist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >IS THIS THE WAY IT ALWAYS ENDS?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Database Thriller. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness first-hand the horror genres that evolved alongside the digital world. Different corners of the internet tied by one story-line. One tragedy. One team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLICK ?? AWAY TO SURVIVE. FORWARD THE EMAIL? Find the hidden LINKS TO-----</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>--ror genres that evolved alongside the digital world. Different corners of the internet tied byyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy-</i>-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/1259a460dbb2cdd0f72ab8752919bdf0.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/1259a460dbb2cdd0f72ab8752919bdf0.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/1259a460dbb2cdd0f72ab8752919bdf0.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story of three developers, and <i>and</i> what it <strong>it</strong> takes to . A story of three developers,<br><br>                                             three developers, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     t hr<i><u>ee develo pers ,</u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/d09dc0a8e7cd89df99ba0b2c42785f71.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/d09dc0a8e7cd89df99ba0b2c42785f71.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/d09dc0a8e7cd89df99ba0b2c42785f71.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/6b543d960ac61c27c02de60a27dc12fc.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/6b543d960ac61c27c02de60a27dc12fc.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/6b543d960ac61c27c02de60a27dc12fc.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Memories begin to unravel.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The worst aspects of y/our Internet nostalgia put together for you to experience all over again in <strong>oneway.exe</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/3178afd00d5f767c2f9a5f2cb4fa7588.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/3178afd00d5f767c2f9a5f2cb4fa7588.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/3178afd00d5f767c2f9a5f2cb4fa7588.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/6efab7e2ab64933400df6e0bb87eba1b.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/6efab7e2ab64933400df6e0bb87eba1b.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/6efab7e2ab64933400df6e0bb87eba1b.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/22ea85013d4ebb3b76f74fc188fe9886.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/22ea85013d4ebb3b76f74fc188fe9886.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/22ea85013d4ebb3b76f74fc188fe9886.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/1519ac640a86f38573b26983bea1e232.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/1519ac640a86f38573b26983bea1e232.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/1519ac640a86f38573b26983bea1e232.mp4?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&gt; Who are you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/fbeaa9cfc77f7ba023239fa6f0bdc22f.poster.avif?t=1772189371\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349570/extras/fbeaa9cfc77f7ba023239fa6f0bdc22f.webm?t=1772189371\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frame-by-frame animated cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple different endings. Is it the way it always ends for you?  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive fully 3D world for you to explore. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >kitty's your best friend ! :3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't you have another best friend?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your actions will have consequences.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully voiced dialogue. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original music by Marcy Nabors, known for her work in Homestuck, Hiveswap, and Deltarune.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's just fiction.</p></li></ul>",
